price: Sila isaan gara Dachii hin ilaallee akka nuti gosoota gaggaarii hunda irraa meeqaatama ishee keessatti biqilchine?
arabic: أَوَلَمۡ يَرَوۡاْ إِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَمۡ أَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا مِن كُلِّ زَوۡجٖ كَرِيمٍ

version.title: Oromo translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Oromo by Ghaly Ababour Abaghuna, printed in 2009.

meta.transliteration: awalam yaraw ilā al-arḍi kam anbatnā fīhā min kulli zawjin karīmin
